description:
RealSimpleEDU.com brings you on-the-go learning and reference for Geometry

App offers quizzes and tutorials  to help you learn Geometry

App is continuously updated based on your feedback.Your 100% satisfaction is guaranteed.

App Tools include search .



Includes following tutorials:

Introduction,
Angles,
Triangles I,
Triangles II,
Quadrilaterals,
Special Quadrilaterals,
Circles I,
Circles II,
Polygons,
Solids in Space I,
Solids in Space II,
Symmetry,
Coordinate Geometry,
Formula for SAT and GRE .


Includes following quizzes:

Quiz on Angles and Triangles,
Quiz on Polygon,
Quiz on Quadrilateral and Solid Space.


Our Vision: Provide on-the-go references that enable our customers to refer, learn and remember; easy to learn, more engaging and most complete.

Our Mission: A RealSimpleEDU app in every pocket.

Please write to us. We would love to improve this app.
